A family in Kilimani is in agony after their daughter went missing on Friday evening. According to her mother, 11-year-old Larissa Michelle was last seen at the Kilimani Primary School playground. She was wearing her school uniform - a blue cardigan and checked blue and white dress. Her mother can be reached on 0723811847 or her grandmother on 0722154976. You can alternatively report to the nearest police station should you spot the missing minor. Click here for the latest political news    